attributes.Long form description: The student is instructed to assemble a stool. First, he takes the screws and washers from the seat, and then he takes the legs, and he takes the key and puts the screw in the middle.Then he takes a screwdriver and screws the 4 screws to the seat, and turns the stool over. Finally, he places the stool on the table and pauses the recording.
